name: FubuWorld
tagline: Welcome to the world of Fubu
body:
### Welcome to the world of Fubu

We are currently in the process of automating the publishing of "FubuWorld" - a project that aggregates the living documentation projects of all Fubu repositories. 

We plan to have this online by mid August, 2013. We're writing the date publicly so that we can laugh at it later.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
